                  "name": "coverImg",
                  "metadata": {
                    "type": "unsplash",
                    "username": "silverkblack",
                    "link": "https://unsplash.com/@silverkblack",
                    "author": "Vitaly Gariev"
                  },
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "height": 400,
                  "fill": {
                    "type": "image",
                    "enabled": true,
                    "url": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1753351051161-21de8728ec17?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&ixid=M3w4NDM0ODN8MHwxfHJhbmRvbXx8fHx8fHx8fDE3NzQyNDczNjl8&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&q=80&w=1080",
                    "mode": "fill"
                  },
                  "cornerRadius": 16
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "F3cjd",
                  "name": "articleContent",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "height": "fit_content(0)",
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 24
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "QJDoY",
                  "name": "artContent",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 24,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "FWN1I",
                      "name": "p1",
                      "fill": "$--muted-foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "In today's digital landscape, Google reviews are often the first impression potential customers have of your business. Studies show that 93% of consumers read online reviews before making a purchase decision, and businesses with higher ratings consistently outperform their competitors in local search results.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "BTL2v",
                      "name": "h2b",
                      "fill": "$--foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "1. Make It Easy to Leave a Review",
                      "lineHeight": 1.3,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 20,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "Aoc1F",
                      "name": "p2",
                      "fill": "$--muted-foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "The number one reason customers don't leave reviews is friction. Create a direct link to your Google review page and share it everywhere — in follow-up emails, on receipts, on table cards, and in your email signature. The fewer clicks required, the more reviews you'll receive.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "f8GUN",
                      "name": "h2c",
                      "fill": "$--foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "2. Ask at the Right Moment",
                      "lineHeight": 1.3,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 20,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "YB5Sc",
                      "name": "p3",
                      "fill": "$--muted-foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Timing is everything. Ask for a review when the customer's positive experience is fresh — right after a successful purchase, a great meal, or a solved support ticket.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "NWZOc",
                      "name": "h2d",
                      "fill": "$--foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "3. Respond to Every Review",
                      "lineHeight": 1.3,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 20,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "6v5QE",
                      "name": "p4",
                      "fill": "$--muted-foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "When you respond to reviews — both positive and negative — you show that you value customer feedback. This encourages others to leave their own reviews.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
